abstract: Malnourished seabirds have been appearing across California in record numbers, pointing to significant changes in ocean's food supply.
lead_paragraph: Malnourished seabirds have been appearing across the state in alarming numbers, some shrunken to little more than feather and bone.

headline.main: California: Number of Starving Birds Rises
